import React from 'react'
import { Box, Typography, TextField, Button } from '@mui/material'
const Register = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Box>
                <Typography>Register</Typography>
                <TextField />
                <TextField />
                <TextField />
                <Button>Submit</Button>
                <Button>Already Registered ? PLease Login</Button>
            </Box>
        </>
    )
}

export default Register
